org.jactr.core.reality.connector

Interface IClockConfigurator

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MasterSlaveClockConfigurator

    public interface IClockConfigurator
    interface accepted by IConnector to tweak how clocks are configured/installed. one of the two getClockFor methods will be called during connection of IConnector. This will occur in the model thread.
    Author:
    harrison
